Title: AN ACT AUTHORIZING THE MUNICIPAL BOARD OF MANILA TO CHANGE THE NAME OF THE CAVITE BOULEVARD TO DEWEY BOULEVARD.
Data:
[ Act No. 2961, February 20, 1921 ]
AN ACT AUTHORIZING THE MUNICIPAL BOARD OF MANILA TO CHANGE THE NAME OF THE CAVITE BOULEVARD TO DEWEY BOULEVARD.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Legislature assembled and by the authority of the same:
Section 1. The Municipal Board of Manila is hereby authorized to order the name of the present Cavite Boulevard changed to Dewey Boulevard.ℒαwρhi৷
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its approval.
Approved, February 20, 1921.
